{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"BroadcastChannel: message event","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/message_event","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel\"><code>BroadcastChannel</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/BroadcastChannel\"><code>BroadcastChannel()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/name\"><code>name</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/close\"><code>close()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/postMessage\"><code>postMessage()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Events</summary><ol><li><em><code>message</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/messageerror_event\"><code>messageerror</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>当频道收到一条消息时，会在关联的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel\"><code>BroadcastChannel</code></a> 对象上触发&nbsp;<code>message</code>&nbsp;事件。</p>\n\n<table class=\"properties\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Bubbles</th>\n   <td>No</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Cancelable</th>\n   <td>No</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Interface</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MessageEvent\"><code>MessageEvent</code></a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Event handler property</th>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/message_event\">onmessage</a></code></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"实时示例","title":"实时示例","isH3":true,"content":"<p>在这个例子中，有一个 <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/iframe\">&lt;iframe&gt;</a></code> 作为发送者，当用户点击按钮之后，会广播 <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\">&lt;textarea&gt;</a></code> 中的内容。同时，有两个 <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/iframe\">&lt;iframe&gt;</a></code> 作为接收者，会监听广播的消息，并将结果写入 <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/div\">&lt;div&gt;</a></code>&nbsp;元素。</p>\n\n<h4 id=\"发送者\">发送者</h4>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> channel <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">BroadcastChannel</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'example-channel'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> messageControl <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'#message'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> broadcastMessageButton <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'#broadcast-message'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nbroadcastMessageButton<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'click'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    channel<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">postMessage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>messageControl<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<h4 id=\"接收者_1\">接收者 1</h4>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> channel <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">BroadcastChannel</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'example-channel'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nchannel<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'message'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  received<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>textContent <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<h4 id=\"接收者_2\">接收者 2</h4>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> channel <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">BroadcastChannel</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'example-channel'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nchannel<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'message'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  received<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>textContent <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"结果","title":"结果","isH3":true,"content":"<p><iframe class=\"dummy\" title=\"发送者 sample\" id=\"frame_发送者\" width=\"100%\" height=\"170px\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/message_event/_sample_.%E5%8F%91%E9%80%81%E8%80%85.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"dummy\" title=\"接收者 1 sample\" id=\"frame_接收者_1\" width=\"100%\" height=\"150px\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/message_event/_sample_.%E6%8E%A5%E6%94%B6%E8%80%85_1.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"dummy\" title=\"接收者 2 sample\" id=\"frame_接收者_2\" width=\"100%\" height=\"150px\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/message_event/_sample_.%E6%8E%A5%E6%94%B6%E8%80%85_2.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/indices.html#event-message","title":"HTML Standard"},{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/web-messaging.html#handler-broadcastchannel-onmessage","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.BroadcastChannel.message_event"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.BroadcastChannel.message_event","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/message_event/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关信息","title":"相关信息","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>相关事件：<code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/messageerror_event\">messageerror</a></code></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"相关信息","id":"相关信息"}],"summary":"当频道收到一条消息时，会在关联的 BroadcastChannel 对象上触发 message 事件。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"BroadcastChannel: message event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"BroadcastChannel: message イベント","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"message","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/broadcastchannel/message_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/broadcastchannel/message_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel","title":"BroadcastChannel"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/message_event","title":"BroadcastChannel: message event"}],"pageTitle":"BroadcastChannel: message event - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}